value:
I cannot see the future... It is nothing
but darkness to my eyes... Oh, Nils...
Lord Eliwood...

I cannot stay here... I cannot allow
something terrible to happen...

I cannot shake the haze from my
mind... Everything is clouded...

If it is my fate to die in the arms of
someone I care for... So be it.

I have done so many things...
So many things that can never
be undone...

Lord Eliwood is not here either,
is he? Tell me, where should I
go? Oh, $Nf...

I feel as though I am fighting in my
dreams...or perhaps...
What is the purpose of this power?

I have no wish to fight anymore... I do
not want to hurt anyone...$k$pI feel as though everything I have ever
cared for...is being swallowed up by
a horrific darkness...$k$pBut you... You are still going to fight,
aren't you, $Nu?$k$pSomehow the threat of this darkness
has not yet crushed your hope...$k$pIf you are able to stand strong in the
face of it...then perhaps I can too...
Maybe I can even find myself again...
No... This is not what I...
I...I want to see Lord Eliwood...
When you're near, I feel...a little more at peace.
